{"tid":1784051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港Online玩家每日鍵盤任務】","createTime":"2019-12-15T11:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T11:29:51.000Z","uid":61831,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e7649248ca5117179652356f0acb2f42f98da26f","tid":1784051,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:13:32.000Z","msg":"在Telegram加入以下Channel/Bot:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hv5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=4c3bb01e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/comp1823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcomp1823&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hv5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=1112dff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/comp1823</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/reddithk_channel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Freddithk_channel&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hv5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=bf4c8508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/reddithk_channel</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hv5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=f01da08b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/5d666da921c4bf89d4620602363f2959.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F5d666da921c4bf89d4620602363f2959.png&h=97362dc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>1. 狙擊TVB廣告商</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/9e089a5a1d8dc52f24270cae3dccce3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F9e089a5a1d8dc52f24270cae3dccce3e.png&h=6306cc69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個Channel每日都會發放本日狙擊對象<br />\n只需要跟link click入去相應既facebook專頁<br />\n派嬲比最頂既post, 同埋貼佢地提供既圖就可以, 順手like同路人既回覆幫助推上頂<br />\n如果專頁有評分功能, 比1星<br />\n<br />\n<ins>2. Copy投訴信</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/4bf80b5f68bd4192be7f7d5759f6f58b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F4bf80b5f68bd4192be7f7d5759f6f58b.png&h=716172f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個Channel會不定期提供投訴信Template比你Send比政府機構<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3. 做Reddit任務</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/7157495e3690a704950c548672b569a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F7157495e3690a704950c548672b569a5.png&h=8021db69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實就係Search &quot;Hong Kong&quot;呢個關鍵字, 去upvote(推)有利我地既post同埋留言, downvote(拉)不利我地既post同埋留言<br />\nChannel亦有提供幾個同香港有關既Subreddit比大家去推/拉post<br />\n如果英文水平足夠, 可以嘗試友善地同外國人溝通<br />\n<br />\n<ins>4. 做Twitter任務</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/68ac1689af56ffce5a6c36487a275e06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gyazo.com%2F68ac1689af56ffce5a6c36487a275e06.png&h=cba504f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個Bot係根據Twitter文宣組Admin既篩選, 提供一大堆有利我地運動既Twitter post link<br />\n入去Like(比心心), 同埋Retweet(唔好Retweet and Comment), 幫佢地推post<br />\n英文水平足夠既話可以留簡短Comment評論下<br />\n自問水平不足就視情況講下Thank you for standing with Hong Kong之類感謝說話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住，呢幾項任務必須多人做，並且持之以恆，先會有效果，每人每日付出少少時間，做左佢，直到煲底相見既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ccd52a0f932ac8cbadcb685a233e66c6d40bbf64","tid":1784051,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd24945484f8248c665579528045a49230184afc","tid":1784051,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34357cc389639d76fa59f715883258aaea4540aa","tid":1784051,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f88ac4288dd34395526f476e00eb39db2fab59","tid":1784051,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1eaf44a9ae3fecfc8527f340386bf6efe679400","tid":1784051,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7729ed26bd854bfe702e16cf283503b8f9322dad","tid":1784051,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:18:23.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc4d2f64d2993d7b03ab6369a008f138f62da15c","tid":1784051,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:18:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3bcfd0b7c3e71cf1996d5ec5bdc862ea95fb33","tid":1784051,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30b79d7bd23a6ae97163edacaf48e78a4a441884","tid":1784051,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8183d184e4b87e2857f3f31b627bb12241352fd","tid":1784051,"uid":61831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/